<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Notification Service</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-/Y6pD6FV/Vv2HJnA6t+vslU6fwYXjCFtcEpHbNJ0lyAFsXTsjBbfaDjzALeQsN6M" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-b/U6ypiBEHpOf/4+1nzFpr53nxSS+GLCkfwBdFNTxtclqqenISfwAzpKaMNFNmj4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-h0AbiXch4ZDo7tp9hKZ4TsHbi047NrKGLO3SEJAg45jXxnGIfYzk4Si90RDIqNm1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login.css">
	<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<script src="/js/aadm.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container main">
		<div class="container header_n no-padding">
			<hr>
		</div>
		
		<div class="middle">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="centered-text">Пользователей в системе: <b>#{nUsers}</b></p>
				if status
							<p class="centered success"> Отправлено! <p>
				if postbackStatus
							<p class="centered success"> Настройка постбэка сохранена! <p>
			</div>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="row justify-content-center">
					<div class="col-xl-4 col-lg-5 col-md-6 col-sm-8 col-8">
						<form method="POST" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="email">Заголовок уведомления</label>
								<input name="title" type="text" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Заголовок уведомления" autofocus>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="password">Содержание уведомления</label>
								<input name="body" type="text" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Содержание уведомления" autofocus>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="password">Ссылка на иконку</label>
								<input name="iconsrc" type="text" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Ссылка на иконку" autofocus>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="password">Ссылка на картинку</label>
								<input name="imgsrc" type="text" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Ссылка на картинку" autofocus>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="password">Ссылка на оффер</label>
								<input name="offer" type="text" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="https://google.com/?click_id={{click_id}}" autofocus>
								<small class="form-text text-muted">Токен может быть любым, {{click_id}} заменяется автоматически на нужное значение.</small>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="password">Страна</label>
								<select class="form-control countries" name="countries">
									<option value="all">Все</option>
								</select>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="password">Язык браузера</label>
								<select class="form-control langs" name="langs">
									<option value="all">Все</option>
								</select>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Отправить</button>
							</div>
						</form>
						<form action="/adm/api/postback" method="POST">
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<label class="form-control-label" for="email">Ссылка на postback трекера</label>
								<input name="postback" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="#{postback}">
								<small class="form-text text-muted">Токен может быть любым, {{click_id}} заменяется автоматически на нужное значение.</small>
							</div>
							<div class="form-group centered-text">
								<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Сохранить настройку</button>
							</div>
						</form>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container footer_n no-padding">
			<hr>
			
		</div>
		

	</div>
</body>
</html>